<!DOCTYPE refentry PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DocBook XML V4.4//EN" "http://www.oasis-open.org/docbook/xml/4.4/docbookx.dtd">
<refentry id="monospace.font.family">
  <refmeta>
    <refentrytitle>monospace.font.family</refentrytitle>
  </refmeta>
  <refnamediv>
    <refname><parameter>monospace.font.family</parameter></refname>
    <refpurpose>The default font family for monospace environments</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <programlisting>
      <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" parse="text" href="syn/monospace.font.family.xml"/> </programlisting>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>The monospace font family is used for verbatim environments
(program listings, screens, etc.).</para>
    <para>Currently this parameter is taken into account only when the xetex
    backend is used, through the <parameter>xetex.font</parameter>.</para>
  </refsection>
  <refsection>
    <title>See Also</title>
    <para><parameter>xetex.font</parameter></para>
  </refsection>
</refentry>
